{"tid":969844,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大象女孩「腳比常人大3倍」　切下8根腳趾只為穿上一雙鞋","createTime":"2019-01-05T10:59:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-05T18:23:06.000Z","uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e84319dab03470878176557153193278c823abf7","tid":969844,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T10:59:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3813/d3813150.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3813%2Fd3813150.jpg&h=c3f0c597&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲大象女孩。（圖／翻攝自每日郵報下同）<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n在一般正常人的生活中，穿鞋、脫鞋就是這麼簡單的事情，但對於印度21歲的珍(Tawheeda Jan)而言，卻是最奢侈的夢想，因為她的腳因為罹患罕見疾病，導致於比一般人還要腫大3倍，生活和走路都有了很大的問題，但其實在全球友大概4000萬有這樣類似的疾病。<br />\n根據英國《每日郵報》報導，珍在出生的時候腳都沒有這樣的問題，然而卻因為生活環境的髒亂，被蚊蟲叮咬而染上了淋巴斯蟲病，也就是所謂「象皮症」，雖說是罕見疾病的一種，但大多集中在熱帶地區，其實有8億人會受到這樣的病症威脅，除了身體、肢體外觀受所損也有失能的可能。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3813/d3813151.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3813%2Fd3813151.jpg&h=0f5ac509&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲奇怪的腳尺寸讓她備受嘲笑。<br />\n珍因為有比一般人大至少3倍的腳，所以也都無法穿鞋，甚至就連走路都是步步艱辛，即便喜歡穿鞋也沒有辦法。13歲時，珍因為學校遷校，所以必須走的更遠去上課，一路上她飽受嘲笑和欺負，因為同學們都叫她「大象女孩」。<br />\n漸漸的珍奇怪的大腳在許多地方傳開，善心人士機構也都帶著募款前往探望，希望她可以得到適當的治療。珍最後接受了當地醫院「切除8根腳趾」的手術，情況才得以好轉，雖然在行走時會感到腳痛，但為了自己能夠穿上漂亮的鞋子，她也努力的復健著。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190105/1348984.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190105%2F1348984.htm&d=FplOXDoFoE1lGW4zee4nEJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=16e24dbd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190105/1348984.htm</a>"},{"pid":"6eefe82d1e92adc6fa711abc3f8f167be219daba","tid":969844,"uid":212399,"like":25,"dislike":2,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T11:03:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4UQhvO9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4UQhvO9.gif&h=b7846a1c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b25f2a8b32f56fa150b2dcca916d52fa43578dcf","tid":969844,"uid":100230,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T11:05:27.000Z","msg":"割足適履"},{"pid":"d917203970041963829a7e75814a5b4ee9f17906","tid":969844,"uid":25468,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T11:07:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg9-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/1509109_1571015936481193_6952286521128396300_n.jpg?_nc_cat=105&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg9-1.fna&amp;oh=0a3ee03d0644a58365335aebd22a0180&amp;oe=5CC4D5FA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg9-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F1509109_1571015936481193_6952286521128396300_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D105%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg9-1.fna%26oh%3D0a3ee03d0644a58365335aebd22a0180%26oe%3D5CC4D5FA&h=17728b42&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"85a2ca6ab553e93b7cf089a016f781fc208ca30d","tid":969844,"uid":121355,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T11:11:06.000Z","msg":"呢啲就一定有圖"},{"pid":"e18365add9d2410ec960471b7d5e57e323f11ed0","tid":969844,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T11:13:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56753c8f12c88dae29f0c08080afd266b72892dc","tid":969844,"uid":208159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T12:15:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d066ddf177011124f7ed2c6dacb2472ecf99e851","tid":969844,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T18:23:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}